    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those points. they're a good start, but for a high-level debate, my students need to go deeper than just \"sovereignty.\" can you flesh those out a bit more? like, give me some more granular, heavyweight arguments—maybe touch on things like economic impact on wages, national security/terrorism concerns, and the strain on social infrastructure. they need to be able to argue these points with real weight so they don't get brushed off easily in the round.",
