      "content": "that's helpful. now, to make sure my students are fully prepared, they're going to hear a lot of counter-arguments that these points are just fear-mongering or oversimplified. how would a debater respond to the claim that the economic and security arguments are basically just outdated tropes used to delegitimize migration? can you give me a strong rebuttal to that specific criticism?",
